snippet.title: Feminist take on Johnny Depp v Amber Heard
snippet.description:
This is a very frank discussion of how the Johnny Depp versus Amber Heard case impacts  discussions on feminism and what it means today, in addition to how domestic violence is handled.
#JusticeForJohnnyDepp #MenToo #DVHasNoGender

•A more detailed discussion of the UK judge’s connections to the opposing team can be found here:  https://youtu.be/mzbwMAj73UQ

•For further info and a very detailed, objective analysis of the evidence (audios, video depositions, text messages, etc.) see and follow Incredibly Average on his channel. 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCg0C-N_MPYYOXyF4T3jMxNQ
